ontent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ytn1665702719008.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ytn1665702719008.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ytn1665702719008.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ytn1665702719008\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determine the result when Uniface compares a numeric space to 0.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__topic_d142319e1_d142320e1_d142321e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__p_d142322e1_d142323e1_d142324e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NUM_SPACE_CMP_ZERO</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__section_q32_h2v_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d155332e68\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__ul_j14_32v_jwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__li_d50102e1_d50103e1_d50104e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>—return TRUE when comparing a\n               numeric operand with a Space (\" \") value to zero; default. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__li_d50105e1_d50106e1_d50107e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—return FALSE when comparing a\n               numeric operand with a Space (\" \") value to zero. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__section_fzb_j2v_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d155332e87\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__table_d17084e1_d17085e1_d17086e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__section_ggq_l2v_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d155332e135\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__p_d142334e1_d142335e1_d142336e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NUM_SPACE_CMP_ZERO</span> determines\n            the value that is returned when Uniface compares a space value (\" \") in a numeric field\n            to 0.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__note_fjc_n2v_jwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Prior to V6, this setting defaulted to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__section_wjg_42v_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d155332e152\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$NUM_SPACE_CMP_ZERO</code></h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ytn1665702719008__pre_wz1_q2v_jwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[SETTINGS]\n$NUM_SPACE_CMP_ZERO = 1</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534260\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534260\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$NUM_SPACE_CMP_ZERO Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determine the result when Uniface compares a numeric space to 0. $NUM_SPACE_CMP_ZERO { = } 1 | 0 Arguments 1 —return TRUE when comparing a numeric operand with a Space (\" \") value to zero; default. 0 —return FALSE when comparing a numeric operand with a Space (\" \") value to zero. Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: 1 Description $NUM_SPACE_CMP_ZERO determines the value that is returned when Uniface compares a space value (\" \") in a numeric field to 0. Note: Prior to V6, this setting defaulted to 0 . Example: $NUM_SPACE_CMP_ZERO [SETTINGS] $NUM_SPACE_CMP_ZERO = 1 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}